{% macro render_coverage_details(language) -%}
#### Coverage Metric Definitions

{% if language == 'python' -%}
**Line Coverage (80%+ target)**
- Percentage of source lines executed by tests
- Tools: pytest-cov, coverage.py
- Helps identify untested code paths

**Branch Coverage (70%+ target)**
- Percentage of conditional branches executed
- Tools: pytest-cov with --cov-branch
- Catches missing if/else and loop conditions

**Function Coverage (90%+ target)**
- Percentage of functions/methods with at least one test
- Tools: pytest-cov
- Every function should have explicit test coverage

**Statement Coverage (85%+ target)**
- Similar to line coverage, counts statements
- Tools: coverage.py
- Complements line coverage for complex statements

**Mutation Testing (80%+ target)**
- Measure of test quality by introducing bugs
- Tools: mutmut, pytest-mutmut
- Verifies that tests catch real defects

**Path Coverage (60%+ target)**
- Percentage of unique execution paths tested
- Complex metric, requires dedicated tools
- Focus on critical business logic paths

{% elif language == 'typescript' -%}
**Line Coverage (90%+ target)**
- Percentage of source lines executed by tests
- Tools: Vitest coverage, Jest coverage, c8
- Essential for TypeScript strict mode projects

**Branch Coverage (80%+ target)**
- Percentage of conditional branches executed
- Tools: Vitest coverage with branch option
- Catches missing if/else and optional chains

**Function Coverage (95%+ target)**
- Percentage of functions with at least one test
- Tools: Vitest coverage, c8
- Every exported function must be tested

**Statement Coverage (90%+ target)**
- Statement-level coverage tracking
- Tools: Vitest coverage
- Fine-grained test verification

**Mutation Score (85%+ target)**
- Test quality measured by fault injection
- Tools: @stryker-mutator/core
- Ensures tests catch real bugs

**Path Coverage (70%+ target)**
- Unique execution paths through code
- Important for conditional logic
- Focus on business-critical paths

{% else -%}
**Line Coverage (80%+ target)**
- Percentage of source lines executed by tests

**Branch Coverage (70%+ target)**
- Percentage of conditional branches executed

**Function Coverage (90%+ target)**
- Percentage of functions tested

**Statement Coverage (85%+ target)**
- Percentage of statements executed

**Mutation Score (80%+ target)**
- Test quality measured by fault injection

**Path Coverage (60%+ target)**
- Percentage of unique execution paths tested

{% endif -%}
